<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>최고 관리자 - SchoolHub Admin</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("../partials/superadmin-header", { school: null }) %>

  <main class="superadmin-page">
    <section class="admin-page-header">
      <div>
        <span class="admin-label">SUPER ADMIN</span>
        <h1>최고 관리자 페이지</h1>
        <p>학교, 유저, 게시판, 분실물 관리 기능에 접근할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="admin-dashboard-grid">
      <a href="/superadmin/users" class="admin-dashboard-card">
        <strong>유저 관리</strong>
        <span>가입한 유저 목록과 권한을 관리합니다.</span>
        <em><%= usersCount %>명</em>
      </a>

      <a href="/superadmin/schools" class="admin-dashboard-card">
        <strong>학교 관리</strong>
        <span>학교 추가, 활성화, 비활성화 기능을 관리합니다.</span>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="admin-section">
      <div class="admin-section-header">
        <h2>학교별 관리</h2>
        <p>학교를 선택하면 게시판, 분실물, 공지, 신고, 승인 기능을 관리할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-school-list">
        <% schools.forEach((school) => { %>
          <article class="admin-school-card">
            <div>
              <h3><%= school.name %></h3>
              <p>/<%= school.slug %></p>
            </div>

            <div class="admin-school-actions">
              <a href="/superadmin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/board">게시판 관리</a>
              <a href="/superadmin/schools/<%= school.slug %>/lost-items">분실물 관리</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include("../partials/admin-footer") %>
</body>
</html>